\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 NEW HIGHEST DUNGEON RAIDING IN THE MACAU}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Players who join the Highmant or Highmountain West factions to fight on behalf of Tauren or Horde}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 will receive a new raid structure: the Highmant, held by the Tauren and Horde.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 This raid structure will allow players to form a powerful}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 monk bond with an NPC ally, and work together to overthrow the current}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 current ruler of Tauren or Horde. These raids will have weekly and daily bonuses and}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 tips, and are intended for a variety of raid composition.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The Highmant will be a hub of Tol Barad and Orgrimmar, the capital city of}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 the Alliance. The Highmountain West faction will extend the Reach and the Eastern Plaguelands}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 of the Horde in order to provide a foothold for the new raid structure.}
