\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0      When a player uses an ability that has a visual effect that resembles a cross-section of the torso, they are viewing a representation of the character's torso in 3D space. The player's head is displayed in left field, while the character's hands and feet are displayed in right field.}
